â™ª my head

40:47.012 --> 40:48.611
Hey, gavin.

40:48.613 --> 40:49.779
Maggie.

40:49.781 --> 40:51.781
I'm pregnant.

40:51.783 --> 40:52.882
Huh? Whoa! (grunts)

40:58.656 --> 41:03.893
â™ª tell me which is which

41:03.895 --> 41:07.697
â™ª prepare my heart for this

