â™ª and I'll say

41:28.085 --> 41:33.723
â™ª I feel like a wrecking ball

41:33.725 --> 41:39.128
â™ª with bottles of alcohol

41:39.130 --> 41:43.933
â™ª but when will the dawn break

41:43.935 --> 41:46.836
â™ª even again?

41:55.779 --> 41:57.180
I saw you...

41:57.182 --> 41:59.282
Talking to yourself.

41:59.284 --> 42:02.685
I... I don't know
what it is.

42:02.687 --> 42:05.989
If you... Really do
see things.

42:05.991 --> 42:07.924
I'll fight, charlie.
I'll fight for us.

42:07.926 --> 42:09.926
I'll... I'll fight
for <i>you.</i>

42:09.928 --> 42:13.763
I know.
